Document: VisualShaderNodeStep
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodestep.rst
Summary: A shader node that returns 0.0 if input value is below a specified edge threshold, otherwise returns 1.0.

Translates to step(edge, x) in the shader language. Returns 0.0 if x is smaller than edge and 1.0 otherwise.
